    Enclosing class:
    CleanerChore<T extends FileCleanerDelegate>

    private class CleanerChore.CleanerTask
extends RecursiveTask<Boolean>
    Attemps to clean up a directory, its subdirectories, and files. Return value is true if everything was deleted. false on partial / total failures.
